videos.headline: Blossomgame's monster jam finishes off Duke

videos.description: Clemson coach Brad Brownell discusses beating back-to-back ranked opponents for the first time since 1989.

videos.description: Bob Wischusen and LaPhonso Ellis break down Clemson's 68-63 win over Duke, its second-straight win over a ranked opponent.
